sequenceDiagram
    participant Browser as Browser / Client
    participant Envoy as Envoy Proxy<br/>(RHOAI Gateway)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant AuthProxy as kube-auth-proxy<br/>(auth mode)<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant RBACProxy as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>(rbac mode)<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant OIDC as OIDC Provider<br/>(Keycloak)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant OSAuth as OpenShift OAuth<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Upstream as Upstream App<br/>(RHOAI Component)
    participant Redis as Redis<br/>6379/TCP

    rect rgb(230, 240, 255)
        Note over Browser,Upstream: Flow 1: OIDC Authentication (auth mode)
        Browser->>AuthProxy: GET /resource<br/>HTTPS/8443, TLS 1.2+
        AuthProxy-->>Browser: 302 Redirect to /oauth2/start
        Browser->>AuthProxy: GET /oauth2/start<br/>No auth
        AuthProxy->>OIDC: Redirect to authorize endpoint<br/>HTTPS/443, Client credentials, PKCE
        Browser->>OIDC: User authenticates<br/>HTTPS/443, User credentials
        OIDC->>Browser: 302 Redirect with auth code
        Browser->>AuthProxy: GET /oauth2/callback?code=...<br/>HTTPS/8443, CSRF cookie
        AuthProxy->>OIDC: POST /token (code + PKCE)<br/>HTTPS/443, Client credentials
        OIDC-->>AuthProxy: Access token + ID token
        AuthProxy->>Redis: Store session (optional)<br/>TCP/6379, Password/TLS
        AuthProxy-->>Browser: Set session cookie + redirect
        Browser->>AuthProxy: GET /resource<br/>HTTPS/8443, Session cookie
        AuthProxy->>Upstream: Forward request<br/>HTTP/HTTPS, Identity headers injected<br/>(X-Forwarded-User, X-Forwarded-Email, X-Forwarded-Groups)
        Upstream-->>AuthProxy: Response
        AuthProxy-->>Browser: Response
    end

    rect rgb(255, 245, 230)
        Note over Browser,Upstream: Flow 2: Envoy ext_authz Integration (auth mode)
        Browser->>Envoy: GET /resource<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.3, Bearer token or cookie
        Envoy->>AuthProxy: GET /oauth2/auth<br/>HTTP/8080 (in-pod), Bearer forwarded
        alt Valid session
            AuthProxy-->>Envoy: 202 Accepted<br/>X-Auth-Request-User, X-Auth-Request-Groups headers
            Envoy->>Upstream: Forward request<br/>HTTP/HTTPS, Auth headers from 202
            Upstream-->>Envoy: Response
            Envoy-->>Browser: Response
        else Invalid / no session
            AuthProxy-->>Envoy: 401 Unauthorized
            Envoy-->>Browser: 401 Unauthorized
        end
    end

    rect rgb(230, 255, 230)
        Note over Browser,Upstream: Flow 3: RBAC Authorization (rbac mode)
        Browser->>RBACProxy: GET /resource<br/>HTTPS/8443, TLS 1.2+, Bearer token
        RBACProxy->>K8sAPI: TokenReview<br/>HTTPS/443, SA token
        K8sAPI-->>RBACProxy: User identity
        RBACProxy->>K8sAPI: SubjectAccessReview<br/>HTTPS/443, SA token<br/>(resource, verb, namespace)
        alt Authorized
            K8sAPI-->>RBACProxy: Allowed
            RBACProxy->>Upstream: Forward request<br/>HTTP/HTTPS/H2C<br/>x-remote-user, x-remote-groups headers
            Upstream-->>RBACProxy: Response
            RBACProxy-->>Browser: Response
        else Denied
            K8sAPI-->>RBACProxy: Denied
            RBACProxy-->>Browser: 403 Forbidden
        end
    end
